Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,At the Hyatt Regency, the\Ndeadly change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:06.62,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,looked like a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The walkway design used\None continuous
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.76,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,hanger rod from roof to\Nfourth floor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.34,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,to second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:14.93,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In shop drawings,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.01,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,it became two shorter\Nrods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.56,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Easier to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:20.11,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But the load path
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.31,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The fourth-floor\Nconnection now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,carried both walkways, not\None.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.77,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The load essentially\Ndoubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:31.34,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,NBS later found the\Noriginal design was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:34.79,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,already weak; the revision\Nleft roughly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:37.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,one-third of code-expected\Ncapacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:41.27,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,On July 17, 1981, two\Nwalkways collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.25,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,during a crowded dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:46.70,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Official records count 113\Ndead and 186
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.03,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,This was not a shop\Ndetail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.21,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was a structural\Nredesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.26,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Every handoff treated it\Nlike paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.96,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
